    @SupportedAnnotationTypes(value="com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.GenDto")
public class GenDtoProcessor
extends GenProcessor
    Processes GenDto annotations.

    GenDtoProcessor should only ever be called by tool infrastructure. See Processor for more details.
